{"title":"孙中山先生九旬诞辰谒陵口占三绝句","authors":["李济深"],"dates":[{"year":1956,"month":11,"day":16}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"孙中山先生九旬诞辰谒陵口占三绝句"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李济深"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十年不谒先生墓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今日来瞻思宛然，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毕竟师俄开觉路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民胜利史无前。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中山陵上树长青，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"民族光辉炳若星，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命成功看今日，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同声告慰在天灵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"盛典空前此谒陵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抚今追昔感难胜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只应善替先生志，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命精神共继承。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}